<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=elphaba89&buddyTimeStamp=20040907&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193059870&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Sami</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Sami lives at <a href='/home/?user=elphaba89'>5940 Broadway Boulevard</a>, Metro Park, which is very close to downtown Millsberry, as well as the Millsberry Academy. Twice a week, after class has let out, Sami and her friends enjoy practicing their acting skills with the rest of the Millsberry drama club. They have a big play coming up soon, so she and her friends are currently practicing very hard.<br><br>After dinner, Sami enjoys listening to music as she plays on her computer. Since she is very creative, and somewhat witty, she can create the funniest things using her computer. Her friends often come by to talk in her room, because it''s so cool. She has a crazy pink sofa to chill out on, as well as indigo curtains-everything''''s in her favorite colors. When she''s not on her computer, Sami likes to play music while chatting with her friends about different topics. Sami can be a bit skeptical at times, but she''s really fun to talk to!<br><br>During her spare time, Sami loves to visit the amusement park with her friends, or walk around the mall. One of her other favorite activities is taking in a movie. Whenever there''s a cool new movie coming out, Sami is always the first in line. As a big fan of show tunes, if the music from a movie is good, Sami will surely go to the mall and buy the CD, adding it to her large collection of music.<br><br>Speaking of music&mdash;whenever Sami is in her room, and awake, she is always blasting her stereo. It''s one of her favorite things to do, just sitting down and chilling with all her favorite CDs. She likes a wide variety of music, ranging from pop to jazz. So... if you like good music, and would be interested in a great person to talk to, stop by and make a friend!</div>
